제주도 스타벅스 매장 지도¶

In [16]:
import requests
import json
import pandas as pd
from pandas.io.json import json_normalize

_ = (33.361666, 126.529166)

data = {
    'ins_lat': '33.4996213', #   
    'ins_lng': '126.5311884',
    'p_sido_cd':'16', # 01=, 08= ... 16=
    'p_gugun_cd':'',  #  (  / )
    'in_biz_cd':'',
    'set_date':'',
    'iend':'1000',
}
    
url = 'https://www.istarbucks.co.kr/store/getStore.do'
r = requests.post(url, data=data)
df = json_normalize(json.loads(r.text), 'list')

map_osm = folium.Map(location=_, zoom_start=10)
for ix, row in df.iterrows():
    location = (row['lat'], row['lot'])
    folium.Marker(location, popup=row['s_name']).add_to(map_osm)

map_osm
